        "changes": "In deviation from the original plan (increasing ARB emissions in three phases), we have decided to distribute the same number of ARB tokens every week (linear emissions). Furthermore, we have planned slightly decreasing emissions for the LP rewards over the LTIPP period and slightly increasing emissions for the trader rewards at the same level. The purpose of this is to initially attract enough liquidity that can then serve as a counterparty for traders. The DEX-LP rewards are distributed linearly from weeks 1-12, with the exception that we only distribute half of the rewards for the first 2 weeks and spread the other half over the remaining weeks.",
        "lessons": "We have learned that many things can change from the application to be included into the LTIPP, to the state of the market and its effect on sentiment, to the user behavior. We will continue to adapt the incentives as we see the individual activities play out for LP, trading, and DEX liquidity.",
