      "planned": {
        "changes": "In deviation from the original plan (increasing ARB emissions in three phases), we have decided to distribute the same number of ARB tokens every week (linear emissions). Furthermore, we have planned slightly decreasing emissions for the LP rewards over the LTIPP period and slightly increasing emissions for the trader rewards at the same level. The purpose of this is to initially attract enough liquidity that can then serve as a counterparty for traders. The DEX-LP rewards are distributed linearly from weeks 1-12, with the exception that we only distribute half of the rewards for the first 2 weeks and spread the other half over the remaining weeks.\nThe metrics have also been adjusted according to the APR expectations set forth in the application and modified for the adjusted ARB price. Discussions have been posted in the governance forum here: https://forum.arbitrum.foundation/t/ipor-protocol-ltipp-application-final/21965/11",
